OL,3,CThe nurses who challenged their
OL,4,Cemployer after 'dignity violated'
OL,6,FEach morning for more than three
OL,7,Fweeks, seven Darlington nurses walked
OL,8,Finto a tribunal to give - and hear -
OL,9,Fevidence in a case that had put them
OL,10,Fin the national limelight.
OL,12,FIt was not a position the women found
OL,13,Fthemselves in regularly.
OL,15,FAs one told me later, "I usually shy
OL,16,Faway from being in the spotlight ...
OL,17,Fso it was quite nerve wracking."
