OL,3,CThe nurses who challenged their
OL,4,Cemployer after 'dignity violated'
OL,6,FAt the start and end of the hearing,
OL,7,Fthere were cameras, banners and
OL,8,Fbackers aplenty - with the latter
OL,9,Fcheering their support as the group of
OL,10,Fseven entered and left the building.
OL,12,FAt other times, the claimants were
OL,13,Fable to enter quietly, no doubt
OL,14,Ffocused on the day, and the issues,
OL,15,Fwhich lay ahead.
OL,17,FThe women were brought together in
OL,18,Ftheir work on the day surgery unit at
OL,19,FDarlington Memorial Hospital.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/11
