OL,3,CThe nurses who challenged their
OL,4,Cemployer after 'dignity violated'
OL,6,FWhat also unites them is their
OL,7,Fdecision to challenge a policy of
OL,8,Ftheir employer, County Durham and
OL,9,FDarlington NHS Foundation Trust, which
OL,10,Fallowed staff to use the single sex
OL,11,Fchanging room of their choice, based
OL,12,Fon the gender with which they
OL,13,Fidentified.
OL,15,FAsk the women what motivated their
OL,16,Factions, and their precise answers
OL,17,Fvary.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/11
