OL,3,CThe nurses who challenged their
OL,4,Cemployer after 'dignity violated'
OL,6,FRose was born male and identifies as a
OL,7,Fwoman, and was free to use the
OL,8,Ffacilities under the trust's
OL,9,FTransitioning in the Workplace policy
OL,10,Fwhich was in place at the time.
OL,12,FThe women bringing the claim maintain
OL,13,Fthat their argument has never been
OL,14,Fwith Rose themselves, but with the
OL,15,Ftrust itself.
OL,17,FAmong several members of its senior
OL,18,Fmanagement who gave evidence to the
OL,19,Ftribunal was its Director of
OL,20,FWorkforce, Andrew Thacker.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/11
