OL,3,CThe nurses who challenged their
OL,4,Cemployer after 'dignity violated'
OL,6,FMr Thacker told the hearing he had a
OL,7,Fresponsibility for staff across the
OL,8,Forganisation and believed the policy
OL,9,Fat the time, which enabled transgender
OL,10,Fpeople to use the changing room of
OL,11,Ftheir choice, was correctly applied.
OL,13,FMr Thacker also described the "vast"
OL,14,Fmedia interest from the spring of
OL,15,F2024, which was sparked by the nurses'
OL,16,Fdecision to go public and his concerns
OL,17,Fover the issue being "played out in
OL,18,Fthe public domain".
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/11
