OL,3,CThe nurses who challenged their
OL,4,Cemployer after 'dignity violated'
OL,6,FWhile much of the evidence came from
OL,7,Fthe nurses and trust managers, the
OL,8,Fappearance of Rose Henderson, towards
OL,9,Fthe end of the proceedings, also made
OL,10,Fheadlines.
OL,12,FThey told the hearing they had used
OL,13,Fthe female changing room from their
OL,14,Ffirst day at the hospital.
OL,16,FRose said it had never occurred to
OL,17,Fthem that using that changing space
OL,18,Fmight be a risk - in terms of making
OL,19,Fothers feel frightened or
OL,20,Funcomfortable.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G7/11
