OL,3,CThe nurses who challenged their
OL,4,Cemployer after 'dignity violated'
OL,6,FThe hearing wrapped up in early
OL,7,FNovember and since then, the three
OL,8,Fmembers of the tribunal panel have
OL,9,Fbeen weighing up the evidence.
OL,11,FTheir findings have now been published.
OL,13,FThere is no doubt this legal case has
OL,14,Fbeen a costly one, from several
OL,15,Fperspectives.
OL,17,FThe nurses' claim was supported by an
OL,18,Forganisation called the Christian
OL,19,FLegal Centre.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G8/11
