OL,3,CThe nurses who challenged their
OL,4,Cemployer after 'dignity violated'
OL,6,FIt has been involved in a number of
OL,7,Fhigh profile employment cases
OL,8,Fnationwide where it believes Christian
OL,9,Fvalues are at stake.
OL,11,FIt is probably fair to say the case
OL,12,Fhas also taken an emotional toll on
OL,13,Fall those involved.
OL,15,FThe lead claimant, Bethany Hutchison
OL,16,Ftold me it had become "all-consuming",
OL,17,Fleading to sleepless nights and
OL,18,Ffeelings of being "robbed" of precious
OL,19,Fmoments with family.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G9/11
