OL,3,CThe nurses who challenged their
OL,4,Cemployer after 'dignity violated'
OL,6,FThe tribunal heard the policy, which
OL,7,Fallowed staff to use single-sex
OL,8,Ffacilities based on self-
OL,9,Fidentification, has since been
OL,10,Fwithdrawn.
OL,12,FIt followed a Supreme Court ruling in
OL,13,FApril 2025 in a separate case, that
OL,14,Fthe legal definition of a woman should
OL,15,Fbe based on biological sex, under the
OL,16,Fterms of the Equality Act 2010.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}       G10/11
