OL,3,CThe nurses who challenged their
OL,4,Cemployer after 'dignity violated'
OL,6,FThe women have long maintained that
OL,7,Fsuccess, for them, would see changes
OL,8,Fin changing room policy - not just at
OL,9,FCounty Durham and Darlington NHS
OL,10,FFoundation Trust but across the NHS.
OL,12,FTheir case itself is now over, but
OL,13,Fwider discussion over who should have
OL,14,Faccess to single sex spaces will
OL,15,Fcontinue.
